#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.22:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Ayoguḷavagga"
msgstr "3. The Iron Ball"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Ayoguḷasutta"
msgstr "22. The Iron Ball"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.22:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn51.22:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn51.22:1.3"
msgid ""
"“abhijānāti nu kho, bhante, bhagavā iddhiyā manomayena kāyena brahmalokaṃ "
"upasaṅkamitā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, do you have personal experience of going to the Brahmā realm by "
"psychic power with a mind-made body?”"

msgctxt "sn51.22:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Abhijānāmi khvāhaṃ, ānanda, iddhiyā manomayena kāyena brahmalokaṃ "
"upasaṅkamitā”ti."
msgstr "“I do, Ānanda.”"

msgctxt "sn51.22:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Abhijānāti pana, bhante, bhagavā iminā cātumahābhūtikena kāyena iddhiyā "
"brahmalokaṃ upasaṅkamitā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But do you have personal experience of going to the Brahmā realm by psychic "
"power with this body made up of the four primary elements?”"

#. VAR: cātumahābhūtikena → cātummahābhūtikena (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn51.22:1.6"
msgid ""
"“Abhijānāmi khvāhaṃ, ānanda, iminā cātumahābhūtikena kāyena iddhiyā "
"brahmalokaṃ upasaṅkamitā”ti."
msgstr "“I do, Ānanda.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.283"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.22:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Yañca kho omāti, bhante, bhagavā iddhiyā manomayena kāyena brahmalokaṃ "
"upasaṅkamituṃ, yañca kho abhijānāti, bhante, bhagavā iminā cātumahābhūtikena "
"kāyena iddhiyā brahmalokaṃ upasaṅkamitā, tayidaṃ, bhante, bhagavato "
"acchariyañceva abbhutañcā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“It’s incredible and amazing that the Buddha is capable of going to the "
"Brahmā realm by psychic power with a mind-made body! And that he has "
"personal experience of going to the Brahmā realm by psychic power with this "
"body made up of the four primary elements!”"

msgctxt "sn51.22:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Acchariyā ceva, ānanda, tathāgatā acchariyadhammasamannāgatā ca, abbhutā "
"ceva, ānanda, tathāgatā abbhutadhammasamannāgatā ca."
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, the Realized Ones are incredible and have incredible qualities. "
"They’re amazing and have amazing qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: samodahati → samādahati (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "sn51.22:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, ānanda, samaye tathāgato kāyampi citte samodahati cittampi kāye "
"samodahati, sukhasaññañca lahusaññañca kāye okkamitvā viharati;"
msgstr ""
"Sometimes the Realized One immerses his body in his mind and his mind in his "
"body. He meditates after absorbing into a perception of bliss and lightness "
"in the body."

msgctxt "sn51.22:3.2"
msgid ""
"tasmiṃ, ānanda, samaye tathāgatassa kāyo lahutaro ceva hoti mudutaro ca "
"kammaniyataro ca pabhassarataro ca."
msgstr ""
"At that time his body becomes lighter, softer, more workable, and more "
"radiant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.22:4.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, ayoguḷo divasaṃ santatto lahutaro ceva hoti mudutaro ca "
"kammaniyataro ca pabhassarataro ca;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was an iron ball that had been heated all day. It’d become "
"lighter, softer, more workable, and more radiant."

msgctxt "sn51.22:4.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, ānanda, yasmiṃ samaye tathāgato kāyampi citte samodahati, "
"cittampi kāye samodahati, sukhasaññañca lahusaññañca kāye okkamitvā viharati;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, sometimes the Realized One immerses his body in his mind "
"and his mind in his body. He meditates after absorbing into a perception of "
"bliss and lightness in the body."

msgctxt "sn51.22:4.3"
msgid ""
"tasmiṃ, ānanda, samaye tathāgatassa kāyo lahutaro ceva hoti mudutaro ca "
"kammaniyataro ca pabhassarataro ca."
msgstr ""
"At that time his body becomes lighter, softer, more workable, and more "
"radiant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.22:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, ānanda, samaye tathāgato kāyampi citte samodahati, cittampi kāye "
"samodahati, sukhasaññañca lahusaññañca kāye okkamitvā viharati;"
msgstr ""
"Sometimes the Realized One immerses his body in his mind and his mind in his "
"body. He meditates after absorbing into a perception of bliss and lightness "
"in the body."

msgctxt "sn51.22:5.2"
msgid ""
"tasmiṃ, ānanda, samaye tathāgatassa kāyo appakasireneva pathaviyā vehāsaṃ "
"abbhuggacchati, "
msgstr "At that time his body easily rises up from the ground into the air. "

msgctxt "sn51.22:5.3"
msgid ""
"so anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti, bahudhāpi "
"hutvā eko hoti … pe … yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti."
msgstr ""
"He wields the many kinds of psychic power: multiplying himself and becoming "
"one again … controlling the body as far as the Brahmā realm."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.284"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.22:6.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, tūlapicu vā kappāsapicu vā lahuko vātūpādāno "
"appakasireneva pathaviyā vehāsaṃ abbhuggacchati;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a light tuft of cotton-wool or kapok. Taken up by the "
"wind, it would easily rise up from the ground into the air."

msgctxt "sn51.22:6.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, ānanda, yasmiṃ samaye tathāgato kāyampi citte samodahati, "
"cittampi kāye samodahati, sukhasaññañca lahusaññañca kāye okkamitvā viharati;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, sometimes the Realized One immerses his body in his mind "
"and his mind in his body. He meditates after absorbing into a perception of "
"bliss and lightness in the body."

msgctxt "sn51.22:6.3"
msgid ""
"tasmiṃ, ānanda, samaye tathāgatassa kāyo appakasireneva pathaviyā vehāsaṃ "
"abbhuggacchati, "
msgstr "At that time his body easily rises up from the ground into the air. "

msgctxt "sn51.22:6.4"
msgid ""
"so anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti … pe … "
"yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattetī”ti."
msgstr ""
"He wields the many kinds of psychic power: multiplying himself and becoming "
"one again … controlling the body as far as the Brahmā realm.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.22:6.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
